methods.name: public XObject operate(XObject left, XObject right) throws javax.xml.transform.TransformerException
methods.comment:
* Apply the operation to two operands, and return the result.
   *
   *
   * @param left non-null reference to the evaluated left operand.
   * @param right non-null reference to the evaluated right operand.
   *
   * @return non-null reference to the XObject that represents the result of the operation.
   *
   * @throws javax.xml.transform.TransformerException

methods.name: public boolean bool(XPathContext xctxt) throws javax.xml.transform.TransformerException
methods.comment:
* Execute a binary operation by calling execute on each of the operands,
   * and then calling the operate method on the derived class.
   *
   *
   * @param xctxt The runtime execution context.
   *
   * @return The XObject result of the operation.
   *
   * @throws javax.xml.transform.TransformerException
